  "result": "Profile heap. `node --inspect`, Chrome DevTools → Memory → heap snapshot. Take 2+ snapshots, diff retained size.\n\nCommon causes:\n- Unbounded caches/Maps → use `LRUCache` or WeakMap\n- Event listeners not removed → `off()` on cleanup, check `emitter.listenerCount()`\n- Closures holding big refs → null out after use\n- Timers (`setInterval`) not cleared → `clearInterval` on shutdown\n- Global arrays grow forever → cap size\n- Require cache bloat → lazy import\n\nQuick check: `process.memoryUsage().heapUsed` over time. Rising = leak.\n\nFix loop: snapshot → diff → find retainer → cut ref → verify.",
